<td align="center"><b>
<i>Megachile comata</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cresson, 1872</font></b><br>
<small><i>Megachile texana_homonym </i>Cresson, 1878, female not male; <i>Megachile armata </i>Smith, 1879; <i>Megachile valida </i>Smith, 1879; <i>Megachile paratexana </i>Mitchell, 1930, replacement name; <i>Megachile &#40;Xanthosarus&#41; valida </i>Smith, 1879</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Megachilidae">Megachilidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Megachile">Megachile</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Xanthosarus&name=Megachile&flags=subgenus:"><i>Xanthosarus</i></a></small>
